---
title: Double Steak and Horseradish Cheese Sauce with Parmesan Roasted Potatoes and Snap Peas
description: Steak and horseradish were born to be together! We won't be surprised if you want to drench your plate in the accompanying creamy cheese sauce, which softens the peppery horseradish.
